# OpenLayers ↔ CesiumJS Adapter Library

React + Vite + TypeScript ile 2D OpenLayers haritalarını 3D CesiumJS sahnesine senkronize eden adapter kütüphanesi.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Project Setup

#### [NEW] Vite + React + TypeScript Scaffold

- `npx -y create-vite@latest ./ --template react-ts` ile proje oluşturulacak
- Bağımlılıklar:
  - `ol` (OpenLayers)
  - `cesium` (CesiumJS)
  - `resium` (React-Cesium bindings)
  - `vite-plugin-cesium` (Vite Cesium static asset/worker config)

#### [NEW] [vite.config.ts](file:///e:/Codes/denemeler/custom_ol_cesium/vite.config.ts)

- `vite-plugin-cesium` entegrasyonu
- Cesium static asset ve worker konfigürasyonu

---

### 2. TypeScript Types

#### [NEW] [adapter.d.ts](file:///e:/Codes/denemeler/custom_ol_cesium/src/types/adapter.d.ts)

- `OlCesiumAdapterProps` — Ana adapter component prop tipi
- `ViewState` — center, zoom, rotation, tilt, extent
- `VectorOptions` — extrude, label, billboard
- `StyleOptions` — circleToBillboard, fillToPolygon, strokeToPolyline
- `LayerMapping` — OL Layer ↔ Cesium layer eşlemesi
- Generic tipler: `ConvertedLayer<T>`, `ConvertedFeature<T>`

