### 3. Utility Converters

#### [NEW] [layerConverters.ts](file:///e:/Codes/denemeler/custom_ol_cesium/src/utils/layerConverters.ts)

| OL Layer | → Cesium |
|---|---|
| `TileLayer (XYZ)` | `UrlTemplateImageryProvider` |
| `TileLayer (WMS)` | `WebMapServiceImageryProvider` |
| `TileLayer (WMTS)` | `WebMapTileServiceImageryProvider` |
| `ImageLayer` | `SingleTileImageryProvider` |
| `VectorLayer` | `CustomDataSource` (entities) |

- Visibility, opacity, z-index sync
- Lazy conversion: sadece görünür katmanlar dönüştürülür

#### [NEW] [vectorConverters.ts](file:///e:/Codes/denemeler/custom_ol_cesium/src/utils/vectorConverters.ts)

| OL Geometry | → Cesium Entity |
|---|---|
| `Point` | `Billboard` / `Point` |
| `LineString` | `Polyline` |
| `Polygon` | `Polygon` (+ extrude height) |
| `MultiPoint/MultiLine/MultiPolygon` | Multiple entities |
| `Circle` | `EllipseGraphics` |

- GeoJSON feature → Entity dönüşümü
- Label / Billboard mapping
- Batch conversion for large datasets

#### [NEW] [styleConverters.ts](file:///e:/Codes/denemeler/custom_ol_cesium/src/utils/styleConverters.ts)

| OL Style | → Cesium |
|---|---|
| `Fill` | `ColorMaterialProperty` |
| `Stroke` | `PolylineMaterial` + width |
| `Circle` | `Billboard` (icon) |
| `Text` | `LabelGraphics` |
| `Icon` | `BillboardGraphics` |

- Color/opacity mapping (OL rgba → Cesium Color)

---

### 4. Hooks

#### [NEW] [useOlCesium.ts](file:///e:/Codes/denemeler/custom_ol_cesium/src/hooks/useOlCesium.ts)

- `useCameraSync(olMap, cesiumViewer)` — İki yönlü kamera senkronizasyonu
  - OL View change → Cesium Camera update
  - Cesium Camera move → OL View update
  - Debounce ile infinite loop önleme
- `useLayerSync(olMap, cesiumViewer)` — Katman ekleme/silme/visibility sync
- `useInteractionSync(olMap, cesiumViewer)` — Click, hover, select eşlemesi

